I. INSTALL

install libapreq2, firebird
perl require File::Base, JSON, DBI


II. CONFIGURE

* configure apache2 (/etc/apache2/vhosts.d/00_default_vhost.conf):
...
<VirtualHost *:80>
    ServerName server.smallworld
    Include /etc/apache2/vhosts.d/smallworld.include
</VirtualHost>

* configure apache2 (/etc/apache2/vhosts.d/smallworld.include):
DocumentRoot "/var/www/SmallWorld/server"
PerlRequire "/var/www/SmallWorld/server/startup.pl"
<Directory "/var/www/SmallWorld/server">
    SetHandler perl-script
    PerlResponseHandler Dispatcher
    Options ExecCGI FollowSymLinks -Indexes
    AllowOverride all
    Order deny,allow
    Allow from all
</Directory>
